#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.bincount.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.bincount"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:1 of
msgid "Count number of occurrences of each value in array of non-negative ints."
msgstr "统计非负整数数组中每个值的出现次数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:3 of
msgid ""
"The number of bins (of size 1) is one larger than the largest value in "
"`x`. If `minlength` is specified, there will be at least this number of "
"bins in the output array (though it will be longer if necessary, "
"depending on the contents of `x`). Each bin gives the number of "
"occurrences of its index value in `x`. If `weights` is specified the "
"input array is weighted by it, i.e. if a value ``n`` is found at position"
" ``i``, ``out[n] += weight[i]`` instead of ``out[n] += 1``."
msgstr ""
"bin 的数量（大小为 1）比 `x` 中的最大值大 1。如果指定了 `minlength`，则"
"输出数组中至少有这么多 bin（但如果需要，可能会更长，取决于 `x` 的内容）。"
"每个 bin 给出其索引值在 `x` 中的出现次数。如果指定了 `weights`，则输入"
"数组将按其加权，即如果在位置 ``i`` 找到值 ``n``，则 ``out[n] += weight[i]"
"`` 而不是 ``out[n] += 1``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:12 of
msgid "Input array."
msgstr "输入数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:14 of
msgid "Weights, array of the same shape as `x`."
msgstr "权重，与 `x` 形状相同的数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:16 of
msgid "A minimum number of bins for the output array."
msgstr "输出数组的最小 bin 数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:19 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The result of binning the input array. The length of `out` is "
"equal to ``np.amax(x)+1``."
msgstr "**out** -- 对输入数组进行分箱的结果。`out` 的长度等于 ``np.amax(x)+1``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:23 of
msgid ""
"If the input is not 1-dimensional, or contains elements with negative"
"     values, or if `minlength` is negative."
msgstr "如果输入不是一维的，或包含负值元素，或 `minlength` 为负。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:24 of
msgid "If the type of the input is float or complex."
msgstr "如果输入的类型是浮点数或复数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`histogram`, :py:obj:`digitize`, :py:obj:`unique`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:29 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:36 of
msgid ""
"The input array needs to be of integer dtype, otherwise a TypeError is "
"raised:"
msgstr "输入数组必须是整数 dtype，否则会引发 TypeError："

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.bincount.bincount:45 of
msgid ""
"A possible use of ``bincount`` is to perform sums over variable-size "
"chunks of an array, using the ``weights`` keyword."
msgstr ""
"``bincount`` 的一个可能用途是使用 ``weights`` 关键字对数组的可变大小块"
"执行求和。"

